    <h2 id="faq">FAQ: NMN vs NR</h2>
    <details class="fq"><summary>Which is better, NMN or NR?</summary><p>NMN raises NAD+ 30-40% faster. NR has more safety data. Both effective at 250-500mg daily.</p></details>
